% Armies Present
% Scenario: move should be chosen in phase(choose).
% - Every territory I own has 1 army (cannot attack: needs >= 2) EXCEPT 17.
% - 17 has 10 armies but its only enemy neighbors (16, 18) have 100 each,
%   so 17*10 < 100*18 => attack is forbidden by the hard constraint.
% - 17 borders friendly 15/19/20, so a maneuver move is the only useful action,
%   which beats pass (move=400 vs pass=5000).
